                    <h4>Low fidelity prototyping</h4>
                    
                    <div>
                        <p>
                            To better explain and get buy-in from management for the layers concept, I created a quick and dirty
                            prototype using <b>Principle</b>.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            This enabled us to move the conversation from vision to practice,
                            as some stakeholders did not fully grasp the concept until they saw it as moving pixels.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </article>

