                            which was until then the official tool for mockups, towards <b>Sketch</b>, a much better tool
                            for interface design that came with shared design libraries as much needed addition.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            The other benefit was a tight integration with Principle, which made creating higher fidelity
                            prototypes a breeze.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </article>

